{"type":"message","id":"4ff6efca","parentId":"b59a1d21","timestamp":"2026-05-03T23:32:44.642Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:443695d7-719e-4ab3-8536-6b2d9a3dd37b Wiki Logging - Emmy] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py emmy\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 7:32 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-03 23:32 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777851164587}}
